<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_Controller_Request_Http::getBaseUrl() return wrong URL if user request URL in this format:
<a href="http://host/index.php">http://host/index.php</a> (index.php in URL).</p>

<p>For example. If user request <a href="http://auto/index.php">http://auto/index.php</a> code:
require_once 'Zend/Controller/Request/Http.php';
$request = new Zend_Controller_Request_Http;
dump($request-&gt;getBaseUrl());</p>

<p>return:
/index.php</p>

    </div>
